@ekelsen, I just checked now, and the code is still in `master`.

I'm not sure how would it break forward compatibility though since `tf.sysconfig.get_link_flags()` would remain internally-consistent - as long as you use Python bits and binaries from the same TF git ref.

Is there a situation when folks use TF binaries from 3 weeks older than accompanying TF Python code?
